---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
---

<section class="scroll-mt-24 bg-brand-ink" id="about">
  <div class="relative">
    <div class="relative min-h-[360px] overflow-hidden lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:left-0 lg:w-1/2">
      <img
        alt="Supporters at a Bernie Sanders event"
        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
        src="/assets/bernie-bg.png"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-ink via-transparent to-transparent lg:bg-gradient-to-r lg:from-transparent lg:via-transparent lg:to-brand-ink"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-2xl lg:grid lg:min-h-[680px] lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="hidden lg:block"></div>

      <div class="bg-brand-ink px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:py-32 lg:pl-16 lg:pr-0">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-lg text-left text-white lg:relative lg:z-10 lg:-ml-28 lg:mr-0 lg:max-w-3xl lg:text-right">
          <h2 class="heading-about mb-4 font-display font-normal text-white">
            A worker cooperative building world-class technology.
          </h2>
          <p class="body-about mb-8 text-white">
            With the Ranks was founded in 2020 by members of the Bernie 2020 technology team, and refined by the movements and organizations surrounding it.
            <br /><br />
            Our team combines decades of organizing with experience from major tech companies, and we’re creating a sustainable alternative to profit-driven software firms.
            <br /><br />
            Our mission is to provide good causes - regardless of their budgets - with presidential quality technology, so organizers can have the tools they need for generations to come.
          </p>
          <Button class="label-button px-8 py-6" href="/about" variant="cta">
            <span>Learn more about our cooperative</span>
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
